            "id": 6312914,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 昭輝(1339)股價拉至漲停，漲停價47.55元，成交223張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昭輝(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1339:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1339\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1339-TW</a>)16日12:06上漲4.3元，股價漲停報47.55元，委買1張，成交223張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為汽車零組件之製造及銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昭輝(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1339:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1339\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1339-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲2.98%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.48%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-9 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-9 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> <li>融資增減：+51 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6312914",
